import "./shipping.css"; import { useState } from "react"; import { useEffect } from "react"; const ShippingFee = ({ sendShippingFee, sendWeight, sendTotalCost, sendDestination, sendPackageType, }) => { const [shippingFee, setShippingFee] = useState(0); const [weight, setWeight] = useState(0); const [totalCost, setTotalCost] = useState(200); const [destination, setDestination] = useState(""); const [packageType, setPackageType] = useState(""); sendShippingFee(shippingFee); sendWeight(weight); sendTotalCost(totalCost); sendDestination(destination); sendPackageType(packageType); const handleCountryChange = (event) => { setShippingFee(event.target.value); setDestination(event.target.options[event.target.selectedIndex].text); }; const handlePackageChange = (event) => { setWeight(event.target.value); setPackageType(event.target.id); }; useEffect(() => { if (shippingFee && weight) { let cost = 200 + shippingFee * weight; setTotalCost(cost); } }, [shippingFee, weight]); return (
